{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "name": "order-lifecycle-demo",
  "spec": {
    "planning_paths": [
      "sdd/01_planning",
      "sdd/02_plan"
    ],
    "canonical_targets_dir": "sdd/02_plan/canonical-targets"
  },
  "commands": {
    "setup": "python3 -m venv .venv && .venv/bin/pip install -q -r requirements.txt",
    "build": "python3 -m compileall -q server",
    "proof": "python3 proof/run_proof.py",
    "ui_parity": "python3 sdd/99_toolchain/01_automation/run_ui_parity.py",
    "serve": "PYTHONPATH=. .venv/bin/python3 server/app.py",
    "e2e": "python3 ../e2e_test.py",
    "deploy_dev": "docker compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d",
    "deploy_prod": "docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d"
  },
  "artifacts": {
    "proof_output": "tmp/proof-results.json"
  },
  "integrations": {
    "github": {
      "project_title": "Order Lifecycle Demo",
      "issue_label": "agentic-dev"
    },
    "discord": {
      "webhook_env_var": "DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL"
    },
    "sdd": {
      "plan_dir": "sdd/02_plan",
      "verify_dir": "sdd/04_verify"
    }
  },
  "notes": [
    "강의 데모용 주문 라이프사이클 서비스. 실재 개인정보 없음.",
    "proof = pytest 결정적 게이트(생성·전환·멱등·화면 parity·회귀). exit 0 = 통과.",
    "10강 실습: build→toolchain→verify 전체를 학습자가 직접 진행.",
    "11강 실습: docker-compose.dev.yml(개발계) + docker-compose.prod.yml(운영계) 배포."
  ]
}
